pip install qrcode[pil]

python make_qr.py 8801234567890

pip install python-barcode[images]

python make_barcode.py 5901234123457

Specify a different format:
python make_barcode.py 1234567890 code128

Specify a custom filename (without extension):
python make_barcode.py "ABC-123" code39 my_custom_barcode
